# Gemini API key for Phase 4 photo capture — keep real secrets out of git.
# Copy Secrets.example.plist → tracklifts/Secrets.plist and add your key
# (or set GEMINI_API_KEY in the scheme's environment for simulator runs).
tracklifts/Secrets.plist
Secrets.plist
# The shared scheme carries a GEMINI_API_KEY env var (a real secret). Keep it out
